um</span><hr size=1> Rules that are not enforce are no longer rules, but suggestions that others have decided to disregard.<br>
<br>
The indignation comes from those with a sense of fair play and dignity. Honesty and Honor are sacrificed upon the alter of the rule book by those that choose to operate outside the agreed upon ruleset. <br>
<br>
Each of us entered the game thinking that the playing field was leveled, each of us had equal chance of earning plat, raising tradeskills, and completing quests/epics. Enter in people that disobey the rules for (even though it is in game) personal gain, and that playing field is no longer level.<br>
<br>
Frankly it no longer becomes a matter of &quot;why should you care what someone does with their money&quot; because at its base level, it could be any infraction of the rules. How would you feel if you realized the other team in pictionary was using sign language to communicate the answer, while drawing jibberish on the board? As the banker in Monopoly would you offer to loan a player a sizable amount of cash at 30% intrest compounded at each passing of GO? Or as a player would you condone it?<br>
<br>
The parable of the automobile speeder was not a bad one, only in that it did not spell it out for the knee-jerk morons who haunt these boards to merely flame posters. <br>
Do people knowingly choose to speed down the road? =Yes<br>
Do they perform this unlawful act cognizant of the possible reppercussions? =Yes<br>
<br>
So what is the difference? Speed and seatbelt laws are enforced. Buying plat and characters, utilizing exploits, and taking unfair advantage of in game bugs ~may or may not~ be enforced. We as isolated individuals behind a mulitutde of computers are not aware of any enforcement of the ruleset.<br>
<br>
You cannot drive down the intersate for more than an hour and not see someone pulled over. The very presence and visibility of the Highway Patrol is in itself a deterrent, and reminder of the consequences.<br>
<br>
Until Sony posts publically that they have shut down people that we all suspect are performing gross misconduct, we will never know. The honest folk continue to feel neglected and impotent, and the dishonest have no evidence that what they are doing will get them caught.<br>
<br>
There is a key word involved here that I have not seen used.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>eth-i-cal:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> In accordance with the accepted priniciples of right and wrong governing the conduct of a group.<br>
<br>
Pure and simple.<br>
If you are breaking the rules, any of the rules, then you are not an ethical person. We cannot condone it, nor should be condemn it.<br>
It is not within our pervue to correct it, that lies with Sony. They have not done enough to police this, and the responsibilty lies with them to do so. To ostrasize or fellow gamers and guild mates only targets the symptom, not the ailment and it the end is futile.<br>
<br>
It is Sony's responsibility to fix this, we either have to suffer through it, or not click on the ACCEPT button.<br>
<br>
Garioch, Last of the Lone Rangers <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=derekeen>Derekeen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://webpages.charter.net/countryquitesuck/eqme.JPG" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 226<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/4/03 5:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4286.topic&index=123>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://webpages.charter.net/countryquitesuck/me.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Buying Platinum</span><hr size=1> Wow! Good post! Couldn't agree with ya more! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=statholturris>Stathol Turris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 406<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/4/03 6:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4286.topic&index=124>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Buying Platinum</span><hr size=1> *sigh*<br>
